<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 00:54:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国和菲律宾寻求更好的沟通和管理南海冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-agree-improve-communication-manage-conflicts-south-china-sea-2024-01-17/</link><description>中国外交部发表声明称，中菲双方同意就南海问题加强海上沟通，通过友好对话妥善管控矛盾分歧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 23:54:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-agree-improve-communication-manage-conflicts-south-china-sea-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>对于许多中国人来说，经济感觉正陷入衰退</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/many-china-economy-feels-like-it-is-recession-2024-01-17/</link><description>中国公务员考试前一天晚上，张美乐焦急地在宿舍走廊里来回踱步，排练答案。回到房间后，她才发现自己一直在哭。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 23:07:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/many-china-economy-feels-like-it-is-recession-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>大连职业足球俱乐部因“历史债务”而关闭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/dalian-pro-latest-chinese-super-league-club-close-due-historical-debts-2024-01-17/</link><description>中超球队大连人队因未能获得下赛季的牌照，宣布立即解散。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 21:21:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/dalian-pro-latest-chinese-super-league-club-close-due-historical-debts-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国商务部官员称，违反出口管制行为将受到更高处罚</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/higher-penalties-coming-export-control-violations-us-commerce-official-2024-01-17/</link><description>美国商务部一名官员周二晚间表示，美国政府将严厉打击违反出口规定的公司，并采取更严厉的处罚措施，以阻止未来涉及中国、俄罗斯和伊朗等国家的违规行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 15:39:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/higher-penalties-coming-export-control-violations-us-commerce-official-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告选举后中国首次重大军事活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-first-major-post-election-chinese-military-activity-2024-01-17/</link><description>台湾国防部表示，周三发现18架中国空军飞机在台湾周边活动，并与中国军舰进行“联合战备巡逻”，这是台湾大选后的首次大规模军事活动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 14:33:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-first-major-post-election-chinese-military-activity-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理访问爱尔兰着眼深化经济联系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/visit-ireland-chinese-premier-eyes-deeper-economic-ties-2024-01-17/</link><description>李强总理周三在都柏林访问期间表示，中国愿深化与爱尔兰的经贸合作，特别是在绿色技术和数字经济等“潜力巨大”的领域。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 13:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/visit-ireland-chinese-premier-eyes-deeper-economic-ties-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>印度拒绝铁矿石开采商NMDC关于向中国出口铁矿石的提议——消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-rejects-iron-ore-miner-nmdcs-proposal-china-exports-sources-2024-01-17/</link><description>三位知情人士称，印度政府拒绝了国有铁矿石开采商 NMDC Ltd 向全球最大铁矿石消费国中国出口矿石的请求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 12:35:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-rejects-iron-ore-miner-nmdcs-proposal-china-exports-sources-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾国防部长斥中国官员“低级言论”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-defence-minister-calls-out-china-official-gutter-level-talk-2024-01-17/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周三指责一名中国外交部官员在新闻发布会上侮辱小费迪南德·马科斯总统，屈尊发表他所谓的“低级和下流言论”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 11:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-defence-minister-calls-out-china-official-gutter-level-talk-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>独家：比亚迪因泄漏问题将停止为其混合动力电动汽车生产软包电池</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-stop-making-pouch-batteries-its-hybrid-evs-leakage-concerns-sources-2024-01-17/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国比亚迪计划停止生产其最畅销的混合动力汽车中使用的袋式电池，因为该汽车制造商寻求解决耐用性问题和电池可能泄漏的风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:10:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-stop-making-pouch-batteries-its-hybrid-evs-leakage-concerns-sources-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国上汽集团将新增14艘汽车船以促进出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-set-add-14-vehicle-vessels-boost-exports-2024-01-17/</link><description>中国国有汽车制造商上汽集团周三表示，该公司计划在未来三年内为其运输船队增加 14 艘汽车船，以提高海外市场的销量。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:06:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-set-add-14-vehicle-vessels-boost-exports-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>疲软的数据和有限的刺激措施使投资者远离中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/weak-data-limited-stimulus-keep-investors-away-china-2024-01-17/</link><description>中国经济增长的不稳定和房屋销售的再度下滑，加大了投资者避开该国市场的决心，导致股市暴跌，因为外国人在缺乏新的政策支持的情况下退出。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/weak-data-limited-stimulus-keep-investors-away-china-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>2022年，尽管和谈正在进行中，印度和中国军队还是发生了两次冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indian-chinese-troops-clashed-twice-2022-even-peace-talks-were-2024-01-17/</link><description>印度陆军英勇奖颁奖典礼上公布的新细节显示，2022年，印度和中国士兵在喜马拉雅边境沿线至少发生了两次冲突，自2020年以来，印度和中国士兵一直陷入激烈的对峙。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 07:48:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indian-chinese-troops-clashed-twice-2022-even-peace-talks-were-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>首名控方证人在香港出庭指证黎智英</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/first-prosecution-witness-testifies-against-jimmy-lai-hong-kong-2024-01-17/</link><description>第一位在针对香港媒体大亨黎智英的具有里程碑意义的国家安全案件中作证的控方证人周三表示，他受黎智英的指示，号召人们参加2019年的抗议活动，并引起西方民主国家的注意。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 07:47:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/first-prosecution-witness-testifies-against-jimmy-lai-hong-kong-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国降价后，特斯拉在欧洲大幅下调 Model Y 价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cuts-model-y-prices-germany-after-china-price-cuts-2024-01-17/</link><description>特斯拉在欧洲（包括德国）大幅下调了 Model Y 汽车的价格，一周前，该公司因电动汽车需求不确定而在中国降价。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 06:22:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cuts-model-y-prices-germany-after-china-price-cuts-2024-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体从台湾转向瑙鲁后竞相进军瑙鲁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-state-media-races-plant-presence-nauru-after-switch-taiwan-2024-01-17/</link><description>新华社的一名记者周三抵达瑙鲁，这是中国官方通讯社在这个偏远的太平洋岛国放弃台湾转而投向中国后首次踏足这个偏远的太平洋岛国，而中国官方媒体正在竞相扩大在当地的影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 06:16:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-state-media-races-plant-presence-nauru-after-switch-taiwan-2024-01-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>